Package com.example.trialio.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Barcode
    Represents a barcode that a user can scan/register
    BinomialTrial
    Represents a trial of experiment type binomial
    CountTrial
    Represents a trial of experiment type count
    Experiment
    Represents an experiment that users can create or participate in
    ExperimentSettings
    Represents the settings of an experiment, more specifically the description, region, owner, and whether or not geo-location is required
    Location
    Represents a location with a latitude and a longitude
    MeasurementTrial
    Represents a trial of experiment type measurement
    NonNegativeTrial
    Represents a trial of experiment type non-negative count
    Post
    Represents a Post that a user can make for an experiment.
    QrCode
    Represents a QR Code
    Question
    Represents a Question that an experimenter can ask about an experiment.
    Region
    Represents a region where an experiment takes place
    Reply
    Represents a reply to a question on an experiment's question forum
    Trial
    Represents a general trial, experiment type not specified
    User
    Represents a user in the system.
    UserContactInfo
    Represents the contact information for a User.
